---
title: Parsley Crusted Salmon and Potato Salad with tender charred broccoli
description: Potato salad is a dish with German origins variations of which are popular across much of Europe. Its creamy nature makes it a great pairing for fattier types of fish such as salmon. Here, tender charred broccoli brings a pleasing green element to the plate.
